{"text": "\u201cThere is no friend as loyal as a book.\u201d", "tags": ["books", "friends", "novelist-quotes"], "author": "Ernest Hemingway"}
{"text": "\u201cWhat really knocks me out is a book that, when you're all done reading it, you wish the author that wrote it was a terrific friend of yours and you could call him up on the phone whenever you felt like it. That doesn't happen much, though.\u201d", "tags": ["authors", "books", "literature", "reading", "writing"], "author": "J.D. Salinger"}
